# Git

## Commit Convention

```text
  feat, add : New feature
  fix : Bug fix
  build : Build file modification/improvement
  style : Style/theme modification/improvement
  refactor : Code refactoring (feature improvement, logic optimization)
  docs : Documentation related
  test : Testing related
  etc : Miscellaneous changes (minor features or issues)
```
